Industrial Translator Board for the DIO48

This board, in combination with a DIO48 card will provide:

24 optoisolated inputs that can be strapped in groups of 8 for either
sinking or sourcing applications.

24 optoisolated .5 ADC OC sinking outputs in groups of 8 with suppresion
diodes.

This board can be built in quantities of 10 for about $60.00 US
With the DIO card this is about $3.33 per point.

The copyrights are assigned to the MatPLC project and the materials can
be used for any purpose provided that the MatPLC text is not removed from
the board and accreditation is given to the project.

The materials are released in this way as there is no hardware/artwork
license comparable to the GPL. This may change and is negotiable if for
some reason this small restriction causes a problem. 

THe board was designed by Curt Wuollet, Owner, Wide Open Technologies and
questions can be posted to the MatPLC mailing list matplc@matplc.org or
sent to wideopen@ecenet.com and I will forward them to the list.

This archive will be added to as I get the time.

This material is provided without any warranty whatsoever and by using
the materials, you agree to this. The entire responsibility for determining
